1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:03,700
你找我吗
You wanted to see me?

2
00:00:03,700 --> 00:00:05,330
我想知道为什么
May I ask why

3
00:00:05,330 --> 00:00:08,130
自从我掌管这个基地以来
You have not filed a single mission report

4
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:11,630
你从来都没交过任务报告
Since I assumed command of this base?

5
00:00:11,630 --> 00:00:13,160
因为我不交任务报告
'cause I haven't given you any?

6
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:16,460
我对这里作出了一些新规定
As you know, one of the changes I made around here

7
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:20,560
其中包括了每位组员都必须写任务报告
Is to require every team member to file mission reports,

8
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:22,930
而不是只有组长或者科研人员要写
As opposed to only team leaders and science officers.

9
00:00:22,930 --> 00:00:24,630
真的?
Really.

10
00:00:24,630 --> 00:00:25,930
我一点都不知道
I didn't-- I didn't know that.

11
00:00:25,930 --> 00:00:27,860
我来这里的第4天就宣布了
I announced it my fourth day here,

12
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:29,430
是在一个小组的出发准备会上
At an away-team orientation meeting

13
00:00:29,430 --> 00:00:32,100
对任务协议书作出的细节变更
Detailing changes to mission protocol.

14
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:33,100
我参加了吗
Was I there?

15
00:00:33,100 --> 00:00:35,600
是的  这个会议是强制参加的
Yes. it was mandatory.

16
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,160
好像我不太记得...
Because I don't remember--

17
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:38,430
我看到你的
I saw you there.

18
00:00:38,430 --> 00:00:39,760
老实说  想无视你还真有点困难
It's kind of hard to miss you.

19
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:43,830
我的意思是
Look, my point is

20
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:47,760
你在每次任务之后要写任务报告
I want you to file a report every mission.

21
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:50,260
我不擅长文笔
I'm not good at writing.

22
00:00:50,260 --> 00:00:52,800
我预料到你会这么说的
I figured you might say that.

23
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:54,560
用这个
Use this.

24
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,930
这是数码录音机
It's a digital voice recorder.

25
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:58,130
对着它说话  我们会把它连上
Speak into it, we'll plug it in,

26
00:00:58,130 --> 00:00:59,460
