And your report

27
00:00:59,460 --> 00:01:00,760
会被自动记录下来  然后生成文档
Will be automatically transcribed and filed

28
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:01,830
和别人的放在一起
With the others.

29
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,030
我也不太擅长说话
I'm not good at talking, either.

30
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,970
不好意思啊
Oh, I'm sorry.

31
00:01:09,970 --> 00:01:11,100
我跑得太快了点  老兄
Too fast for you, buddy boy?

32
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:13,770
我刚接到疗养院的电话  罗德尼
Nursing home just called, rodney.

33
00:01:13,770 --> 00:01:16,030
他们想要回那个滑板车
They want their scooter back.

34
00:01:16,030 --> 00:01:17,600
滑板车?  我那引擎盖下的可是
Scooter? that is a tri-cell li-po pack

35
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,400
三组的锂离子电池
Under my hood, son.

36
00:01:21,930 --> 00:01:23,170
对不起了  是我不好
Ooh, sorry. my bad.

37
00:01:27,630 --> 00:01:29,330
我要把你踩在脚底
Yeah, I will trample you.

38
00:01:29,330 --> 00:01:30,530
别被你自己的裙子绊倒了
Well, don't trip on your skirt.

39
00:01:33,570 --> 00:01:34,470
没事吧
You okay?

40
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:36,100
他差点就掉下来了
I could have dropped him!

41
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,430
对不起  我不知道这里会有人
Sorry, we didn't know anyone was around.

42
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:37,900
你真的没事吧
You sure you're all right?

43
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:38,970
话说回来
Come to think of it,

44
00:01:38,970 --> 00:01:39,870
你在这儿干嘛
What are you doing down here anyway?

45
00:01:39,870 --> 00:01:41,500
我在哄图门睡觉
Trying to get torren to sleep.

46
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:43,230
我发现抱着他到处走最能让他安心
I find that walking him is the best way to calm him.

47
00:01:43,230 --> 00:01:45,030
他害疝气了吧
Ooh, he's colicky, huh?

48
00:01:45,030 --> 00:01:47,630
凯勒医生说这些症状会消失的
Dr. keller says it's a phase that will pass.

49
00:01:47,630 --> 00:01:49,170
不用担心了  我小时候也得过疝气
Oh, don't worry about it.I was a colicky baby too.

50
00:01:49,170 --> 00:01:51,130
你就学我妈那样好了  让我哭到睡着
Just do what my mom did,which was let me cry myself to sleep.

51
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:52,300
反正又不会恶化
I'm no worse for it.

52
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:55,070
反正
Anyway...

53
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:56,670
我们是轮流抱他走路
We usually take turns walking him,

54
00:01:56,670 --> 00:01:58,100
但迦楠去视察民情了
But kanaan is away visiting our people

55
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:59,230
他要不在好几天
For a few days.

56
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:01,730
我很想帮你  但好像
I'd help you out, but it looks

57
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:03,330
你已经把一切问题都解决了
Like you've got everything taken care of.

58
00:02:03,330 --> 00:02:06,570
是的  我现在正要把他带回房间
Yes. now all I have to do is get him back to my quarters

59
00:02:06,570 --> 00:02:08,370
不能吵醒他
Without waking him...

60
00:02:08,370 --> 00:02:10,700
更不能被汽车压到
Or being run over.

61
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,770
我们不玩了
Yeah, we're done here.

62
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:14,600
我们就快结束了
We're just, you know, finishing up,

63
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,870
真的
Really, so...

64
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:16,700
晚安
'night.

65
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,700
晚安  好梦
'night. good one.

66
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,930
冲冲冲冲冲
Go, go, go, go, go, go, go!

67
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:46,330
我好像把马达用过头了
I must have put too much strain on the motor.

68
00:02:46,970 --> 00:02:49,470
得给轴上一点润滑油
Shaft needs a bushing lube.

69
00:02:49,970 --> 00:02:51,030
干嘛
What?

70
00:02:53,730 --> 00:02:55,330
这算什么意思
What's that about?

71
00:02:55,330 --> 00:02:56,400
不知道
Beats me.

72
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,170
瑞迪克
Radek?

73
00:02:58,170 --> 00:03:00,400
进来
Come in.

74
