指挥室  我是麦凯博士
Control room, it's dr. mckay.

75
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:03,230
东区停电了
We just lost power in the east pier.

76
00:03:03,230 --> 00:03:04,730
怎么回事
What's going on?

77
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:18,600
怪了
That's strange.

78
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,770
除了指挥室之外
Lights are out all over the city

79
00:03:19,770 --> 00:03:20,600
整个城市都停电了
Except the control room.

80
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,530
搞什么啊
Why is that?

81
00:03:22,530 --> 00:03:23,770
麦凯博士
This is dr. rodney mckay,

82
00:03:23,770 --> 00:03:24,900
呼叫指挥室
Calling anyone in the control room.

83
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,630
请回话
Please respond.

84
00:03:28,770 --> 00:03:31,230
肯定是出问题了
Something's definitely not right.

85
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:52,930
罗德尼  你在吗
Rodney, are you there?

86
00:04:52,930 --> 00:04:54,300
谢帕德中校
Colonel sheppard?

87
00:05:07,470 --> 00:05:09,100
什么都用不了
Everything's dead.

88
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,430
我们没法调查出了什么问题
There's no way of knowing what the hell's going on.

89
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:11,900
好吧  里维斯
All right. hey, rivers.

90
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:13,070
分散行动
Fan out,

91
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,300
尽可能多找一些船
Find as many marines as you can,

92
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,500
向控制塔上进发
Work your way up to the central tower.

93
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:16,930
如果你碰到伍尔希的话就通知我
If you run into woolsey, let me know.

94
00:05:16,930 --> 00:05:18,230
通讯设施瘫痪了  我们用对讲机
Communications are down. we're on walkies.

95
00:05:18,230 --> 00:05:19,800
瑞迪克
Radek!

96
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,870
罗德尼  怎么回事
Rodney, what's going on?

97
00:05:20,870 --> 00:05:22,100
什么  你也不知道?
What, you don't know either?

98
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:22,930
我准备去控制塔
I'm on my way to the control tower.

99
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,130
还想和你通话呢
I tried to radio you.

100
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:25,030
除了控制塔之外
Power's out

101
00:05:25,030 --> 00:05:26,370
其他地方都没电了  给你
Except for the central tower. here.

102
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:27,630
你干脆去主电室
Go to the main power room instead.

103
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:29,430
看看是不是能重启一下电力系统
See if you can reboot the system from there.

104
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,100
好的
Okay. all right.

105
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,470
好的
All right.

106
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:37,430
是谁
Hello?

107
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:59,400
罗德尼  听得见吗
Rodney, do you read me?

108
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,730
听得见  瑞迪克  你说
Yeah, radek. go ahead.

109
00:06:00,730 --> 00:06:01,930
我试过重启系统
I've tried to restart power.

110
00:06:01,930 --> 00:06:03,700
但目前一点都没进展
So far, absolutely no success.

111
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:05,500
那零点装置呢
What about the zpm?

112
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:06,900
我检查过了
I've checked it,

113
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:07,830
还有Naquadah发电器
As well as the naquadah generator.

114
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:10,170
它们都没联机
Neither are online.

115
00:06:10,170 --> 00:06:12,330
肯定是有人在控制室里把它们拔掉了
Someone must have disabled them from the control room.

116
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:13,770
如果是这样的话
If that was the case,

117
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:15,370
他们自己也会没电的
Then they wouldn't have any power up there either.

118
00:06:15,370 --> 00:06:17,370
他们可能用的是外接电源
Not unless they're using an external power source.

119
00:06:17,370 --> 00:06:19,200
听我说
Okay, listen to me.

120
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,670
你也试试这么做
I want you to do exactly the same thing.

121
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:22,570
启用临时补丁
Initiate a temporary patch

122
00:06:22,570 --> 00:06:24,430
连接外部电源
Using an external power source--

123
00:06:24,430 --> 00:06:25,970
就是那个辅助电池组
One of the auxiliary battery units.

124
00:06:25,970 --> 00:06:27,600
可以  但这点电源维持不了整个城市
Yes, but that won't be enough to power the entire city,

125
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,430
根本不可能
Not by a long shot.

126
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,000
这你别担心
Don't worry about that.

127
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,270
只要给我能启动主机的能量就行
Just get me enough juice to access the mainframe.

128
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:32,600
我们去查一下
We can figure out

129
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,170
那里到底出了什么问题
What the hell's going on up there.

130
00:06:33,170 --> 00:06:34,330
好的
All right.

131
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:35,130
你现在在几层
Whereabouts are you right now?

132
00:06:35,130 --> 00:06:36,700
36层?
Level 36?

133
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:37,700
35层
35.

134
