When we lost power.

150
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:28,230
这门是故意被关死的  好让我们不能进去
It was sealed on purpose to keep people out.

151
00:07:28,230 --> 00:07:29,900
什么  你是说有人在入侵亚特兰蒂斯?
What, you think someone's infiltrated atlantis?

152
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:32,630
罗德尼
Rodney.

153
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,770
说吧
Talk to me.

154
00:07:33,770 --> 00:07:35,200
我启动了临时补丁
I've initiated a temporary patch.

155
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:37,270
我可以把部分的电力传送到你的实验室
I was able to route partial power to your lab.

156
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:39,630
那传输机呢
Well, what about the transporters?

157
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,030
我还在弄
Still working on it.

158
00:07:41,030 --> 00:07:43,330
恢复某一台之后再通知我
Yeah, well, let me know when you've got one online.

159
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:45,630
去实验室试试接进主机
Go to your lab and try to tap into the mainframe.

160
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:47,330
我走另一条楼梯
I'll try the other stairwells.

161
00:07:47,330 --> 00:07:49,200
说不定也过不去  谁知道呢
