169
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:02,400
我们也是
Yeah, so have we.

170
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,230
知道怎么回事吗
Any idea what's going on yet?

171
00:08:03,230 --> 00:08:05,030
麦凯在找原因
Mckay's still working on it.

172
00:08:05,030 --> 00:08:06,730
我估计用c-4能把门炸穿
I guess we could blow the door with c-4.

173
