00:18:44,870 --> 00:18:47,230
别担心  他们快醒了
Don't worry, they'll wake up soon.

396
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:49,470
每个人的抵抗力不同
Everyone has a different level of resistance.

397
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:50,470
来
Here.

398
00:18:50,470 --> 00:18:51,800
谁做的
Who would do this?

399
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:54,030
不知道  我正想查个清楚
I don't know. that's what I want to find out.

400
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,730
你能打开那扇门吗
Can you open that door?

401
00:18:55,730 --> 00:18:56,570
可以
I think so.

402
00:18:56,570 --> 00:18:57,900
好的  上
Good. do it.

403
00:19:10,670 --> 00:19:13,030
还是没反应
Still nothing.

404
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:26,300
泰勒  有段时间你还是挺理解我的
There was a time you understood me, teyla.

405
00:19:26,300 --> 00:19:29,000
我被你们的人带来
When your people brought me here,

406
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:31,700
注射逆转录病毒  将我变成人类
Gave me the retrovirus that turned me into a human,

407
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:35,770
只有你同情我
You alone showed me compassion.

408
00:19:35,770 --> 00:19:38,370
只有你有良心
You were the voice of conscience.

409
00:19:40,870 --> 00:19:44,330
我反复思量
I've given this a great deal of thought.

410
00:19:44,330 --> 00:19:47,830
我...
I've...

411
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:50,500
我想还你个人情
I'm willing to return the favor.

412
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:55,670
我很想带你走
I would very much like for you to come with me.

413
00:19:55,670 --> 00:19:58,130
你可以照顾你的孩子
You can care for your child,

414
00:19:58,130 --> 00:20:00,870
我们照看你们俩
And I will care for the both of you.

415
00:20:00,870 --> 00:20:03,730
我宁愿死
I would rather die.

416
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:08,270
我保证
I promise...

417
00:20:09,670 --> 00:20:13,030
我不会伤害你们的
I will not harm either of you.

418
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:14,000
泰勒
Teyla...

419
00:20:16,670 --> 00:20:18,700
你得相信我
You have to believe me.

420
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:20,730
我不会相信一个杀人犯说的话
I can not trust the word of a murderer.

421
00:20:20,730 --> 00:20:22,800
你怎么就不开窍
Why can't you understand?

422
00:20:24,630 --> 00:20:29,030
我这么做是有苦衷的
I have become what I am out of necessity,

423
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:30,330
生存所逼
The need to survive!

424
00:20:30,330 --> 00:20:32,500
你这么做是为了复仇
You became what you are out of vengeance.

425
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:34,370
难道在你的世界  罪人就不该受罚吗
Do you not punish criminals in your world?

426
00:20:34,370 --> 00:20:36,070
正义就不能得到伸张吗
Are they not brought to justice?

427
00:20:36,070 --> 00:20:37,630
对你来说这是正义吗
Is this justice to you?

428
00:20:37,630 --> 00:20:39,930
杀死银河系数以千计的
Killing hundreds of thousands of innocent people

429
00:20:39,930 --> 00:20:41,030
无辜人民
Across this galaxy?

430
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:42,200
要不是你们要用我来做
They would not be dead

431
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:43,530
那个邪恶的试验
Had you not made me the subject

432
00:20:43,530 --> 00:20:45,330
他们就不会死
Of your vicious experiment!

433
00:20:45,330 --> 00:20:47,530
你的双手沾满他们的鲜血
Their blood is on your hands!

434
00:20:54,370 --> 00:20:55,770
你自己选
It's your choice.

435
00:20:55,770 --> 00:20:58,800
跟我走生存下去  或者留下来等死
You can come with me and live, or remain here and die.

436
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:01,030
无论如何  我都要带走你的孩子
Either way, I'm taking your child.

437
00:21:09,970 --> 00:21:11,730
我们得炸掉飞船
We need to blow up the jumper.

438
00:21:11,730 --> 00:21:13,600
如果我们炸了它
If we blow it up,

439
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:15,400
切断了电源  就停止了力场
We cut the power and disable the force field,

440
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,830
对吧
Right?

441
00:21:16,830 --> 00:21:18,870
好计划  我只是不确定
Great plan-- I'm just not entirely clear

442
00:21:18,870 --> 00:21:20,930
你究竟要怎么炸毁那艘飞船
On how you intend on doing the actual blowing up.

443
00:21:20,930 --> 00:21:21,770
用远程遥控飞船去撞
Fire a drone at it.

444
00:21:21,770 --> 00:21:22,900
不行
We can't.

445
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:24,670
备用电池提供的能量
The chair room requires far more power

446
00:21:24,670 --> 00:21:26,330
无法支撑主室的能量消耗
Than the auxiliary battery units can provide.

447
00:21:26,330 --> 00:21:28,570
我勉强能调足够的能量到这实验室
I was barely able to bring enough power into this lab,

448
00:21:28,570 --> 00:21:29,500
更别提还要支撑几个
Let alone the few transporters

449
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:30,800
刚修好的传输机
I could bring online.

450
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:32,200
好的  那就用飞船
All right, then, we'll take a jumper.

451
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:34,030
我再一次问  怎么做
Again, I come back to my question of how?

452
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:35,500
我们去不了飞船舱
We have no way of getting to the jumper bay.

453
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:37,600
那我们就去水下基地找一架
We'll take one from the underwater bay.

454
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:38,700
飞到塔楼上
Fly it up to the tower,

455
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:40,270
然后扔个飞弹出去
Fire a drone through the window,

456
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:43,130
炸掉迈克尔的飞船
And take out michael's jumper.

457
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,370
怎么了
What?

458
00:21:45,370 --> 00:21:46,800
没  没  听着挺好的
Uh, no, no, no, that's a good plan,

459
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:48,500
除了一个小问题
Except I see one small problem--

460
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:50,430
水下停泊舱
The underwater jumper bay

461
00:21:50,430 --> 00:21:51,770
只有几架飞船
Only has a couple of jumpers in it.

462
00:21:51,770 --> 00:21:53,070
我们只要一架啊
Well, we only need one.

463
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,730
问题是
Yes, well, the thing is--

464
00:21:54,730 --> 00:21:55,730
大多都因长期泡水
Both of them were severely damaged

465
00:21:55,730 --> 00:21:56,670
坏得厉害
In the flood.

466
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:58,430
没有哪架还能飞
Neither of them is able to fly.

467
00:21:58,430 --> 00:22:00,830
都2年了  瑞迪克  麦凯早修好了
That was two years ago, radek. mckay already fixed them.

468
00:22:02,300 --> 00:22:04,470
不会吧...
Oh, you've got to be kidding me...

469
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:05,770
我正准备修
It was the next thing on my list.

470
00:22:05,770 --> 00:22:07,230
你说过你要去修的
You said you were going to fix them.

471
00:22:07,230 --> 00:22:08,870
我知道  我准备要修的  真的
I know, and I was getting to it, I swear.

472
00:22:08,870 --> 00:22:10,300
2年了呢
And you had two years!

473
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:11,830
我忙的很
I was busy!

474
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:13,030
或许我们应该下去看看
Perhaps we should go

475
00:22:13,030 --> 00:22:14,200
还能不能修个一两架
And see if we can fix one of them.

476
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,570
好主意
That's a good idea,

477
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:16,830
但你给我留在这儿
But I want you stay here

478
00:22:16,830 --> 00:22:18,200
想办法切断迈克尔的锁定
To try to override michael's lockouts.

479
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:19,800
为什么我不能留下做这个
Why don't I stay here and work on that?

480
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:20,970
泽兰卡可以和你去修飞船
Zelenka can go with you to the jumper bay.

481
00:22:20,970 --> 00:22:22,600
因为你一定要去
Because I want you to come with me

482
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:24,000
修飞船
And fix those jumpers

483
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,370
你2年前说过
Like you said you were going to do

484
00:22:25,370 --> 00:22:26,370
你要去修的
Two years ago.

485
00:22:26,370 --> 00:22:27,430
走吧
Let's go.

486
00:22:27,430 --> 00:22:28,100
希望有传输机送我们去
Please tell me there's a transporter.

487
00:22:28,100 --> 00:22:29,300
有的
Yes.

488
00:22:29,300 --> 00:22:30,330
不过  离舱远的很
Well, not by the jumper bay,

489
00:22:30,330 --> 00:22:31,970
两层下面有一个传输机
But there's one two levels down.

490
00:22:31,970 --> 00:22:34,530
太好了
That'll do.

491
00:22:42,330 --> 00:22:43,570
干得好
Nice.

492
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:10,130
你会打?
You can fight.

493
00:23:10,130 --> 00:23:13,030
打过5年拳击
Five years of kick-boxing.

494
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:14,930
这消息不错
That's good to know.

495
00:23:14,930 --> 00:23:17,100
发生了什么事
What happened?

496
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,730
是迈克尔和他的变种人
It's Michael and his hybrids.

497
00:23:59,730 --> 00:24:00,970
我数出三个
I counted three of 'em.

498
00:24:00,970 --> 00:24:01,970
不知道后面是不是还有更多的
I'm not sure how many more there are.

499
00:24:01,970 --> 00:24:03,170
估计不会太多
Probably not too many--

500
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:04,330
毕竟是乘飞船过来
They all had to fit in that jumper.

501
00:24:04,330 --> 00:24:07,670
除非他们走过来
Unless more came through on foot afterward.

502
00:24:07,670 --> 00:24:09,670
我们怎么办
What do we do?

503
00:24:09,670 --> 00:24:10,800
先想办法去武器库
Try to get to the armory,

504
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,530
然后回来夺回星门室
come back and retake the gate room.

505
00:24:12,530 --> 00:24:13,670
听起来计划不错
Sounds like a plan.

506
00:24:13,670 --> 00:24:14,670
你们两个  跟我们来
You two, come with us.

507
00:24:14,670 --> 00:24:17,270
你就和他们呆一起  安抚下他们
Stay here with them, keep all of them calm

508
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:18,730
如果还有变种人出现
And, uh, if any more hybrids show up,

509
00:24:18,730 --> 00:24:21,600
就像刚刚那样做
just do what you did earlier.

510
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:30,230
再跟你说一遍  这很紧急
...speak with you again. It's urgent.

511
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:32,330
和他待一起
Stay with him.

512
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,870
怎么了
What is it?

513
00:24:38,870 --> 00:24:40,170
我们终于破译了
We were finally able to

514
00:24:40,170 --> 00:24:42,900
自毁装置的密码
decipher the encryption on the self-destruct device.

515
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,570
很好
Good.

516
00:24:44,570 --> 00:24:46,630
准备起飞
Prepare the ship to leave.

517
00:24:46,630 --> 00:24:48,470
准备启动自毁装置
We'll arm the self-destruct,

518
00:24:48,470 --> 00:24:50,500
然后在我们离开前的瞬间
And switch the power back to Atlantis' systems

519
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:51,930
把电源切回到亚特兰蒂斯的系统
a split-second before we leave.

520
00:24:51,930 --> 00:24:54,700
时机一定要精准
The timing of the switch must be precise.

521
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:56,100
我不想他们有任何机会
I don't want to give them any opportunity

522
00:24:56,100 --> 00:24:57,700
解除装置
to disarm the device.

523
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:59,600
我会计算好的
I'll make the calculations.

524
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:05,170
计划有变
Change of plans.

525
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:06,170
我们不去武器库了
We're not going to the armory.

526
00:25:06,170 --> 00:25:07,370
为什么  发生什么事了
Why? What happened?

527
00:25:07,370 --> 00:25:09,300
他们启动了自毁装置
They armed the self-destruct.

528
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:12,230
伍尔希先生  能否请你回到其他人那里
Mr. Woolsey, would you please head back to the others?

529
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,630
谢帕德中校  我是泰勒
Colonel Sheppard, this is Teyla.

530
00:25:29,630 --> 00:25:31,400
能听得到吗
Can you hear me?

531
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:33,630
约翰  我是泰勒  请回话
John, this is Teyla. Please respond.

532
00:25:49,870 --> 00:25:51,800
谢帕...
Colonel Shep--

533
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:52,800
谢帕德中校
Colonel Sheppard.

534
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:54,300
若楠在控制室
Ronon is in the control room.

535
00:25:54,300 --> 00:25:55,370
正和迈克尔打着呢
He's fighting with Michael!

536
00:25:55,370 --> 00:25:58,530
我们快到飞船舱了  有情况随时通报
We're almost at the jumper bay. Keep us posted.

537
00:26:10,870 --> 00:26:12,070
泰勒  快跑
Teyla, run!

538
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:25,600
泰勒
Teyla!

539
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:26,430
你还好吗
Are you all right?

540
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:27,470
还好
Yes.

541
00:26:27,470 --> 00:26:28,270
但是若楠需要帮忙
But Ronon needs our help.

542
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:29,970
我们必须尽快回到控制室
We need to get back up to the control room.

543
00:26:55,570 --> 00:26:58,830
瑞迪克?  那里发生了什么事
Radek? Tell us what's going on up there.

544
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:00,930
我说不好  若楠倒下了
I-- I can't tell. Ronon is down.

545
00:27:00,930 --> 00:27:03,130
可能昏过去了
He might just be unconscious.

546
00:27:03,130 --> 00:27:05,370
他醒过来了就告诉我
Tell me when he comes to.

547
00:27:05,370 --> 00:27:06,300
我们进展怎么样
What have we got?

548
00:27:06,300 --> 00:27:07,970
就像我说的  两个飞船都坏了
It's like I said--both of the jumpers are toast.

549
00:27:07,970 --> 00:27:09,130
这个有一大堆的问题
This one's got a whole whack of problems,

550
00:27:09,130 --> 00:27:10,600
首先就是没有能源
starting with zero power.

551
00:27:10,600 --> 00:27:12,730
你的意思是说另外一个有能源的对不对
You said the other jumper's got power, right?

552
00:27:12,730 --> 00:27:13,600
对  不过好不了多少
Yeah, but not much else.

553
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:15,430
驾驶舱不能用  也没有飞弹
Drive pods won't extend, there's no drones...

554
00:27:15,430 --> 00:27:16,630
可是这艘有飞弹
This one's got drones.

555
00:27:16,630 --> 00:27:17,970
如果我们把能源弄过来
So if we bring power over to this,

556
00:27:17,970 --> 00:27:19,470
这样驾驶舱就可以用了  对吧
We can get drive pods working, right?

557
00:27:19,470 --> 00:27:21,000
你想让我把两个船上能用的部件
You want me to harvest parts from both jumpers,

558
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,570
就这么拼成一个可以用的飞船?
Cobble together a fix so one of them will work?

559
00:27:22,570 --> 00:27:23,530
可行吗
Is it possible?

560
00:27:23,530 --> 00:27:24,270
我怀疑
Doubtful.

561
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:25,170
但也是有可能的...
But maybe...

562
00:27:25,170 --> 00:27:26,270
怎么说都有很多工作
A long shot at best.

563
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:27,670
很好  开始吧
Perfect. Get to it.

564
00:27:27,670 --> 00:27:28,930
要多久  15分钟?
What do you need, 15 minutes?

565
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:36,270
真好  真是好极了
Great, just great.

566
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:43,230
传输机也被关了
Must've locked out the transporters.

567
00:27:43,230 --> 00:27:44,370
我们要去控制室
We need to get to the control room.

568
00:27:44,370 --> 00:27:45,470
这太危险了  没有武器就不能去
It's too dangerous.Not without weapons.

569
00:27:45,470 --> 00:27:47,170
最近的楼梯在哪里
Where's the nearest stairwell?

570
00:27:47,170 --> 00:27:49,070
转角那儿  这边
Around the corner. This way.

571
00:27:49,070 --> 00:27:51,100
我走前面
Let me lead.

572
00:29:36,270 --> 00:29:39,430
好了  输好了
Okay, give 'er.

573
00:29:40,630 --> 00:29:42,030
驾驶舱可以用了
Drive pods are go.

574
00:29:42,030 --> 00:29:44,570
好了  我们差不多了
All right, now we're getting somewhere.

575
00:29:44,570 --> 00:29:47,130
有能源  有生命支持系统  有...
I got juice, I got life support, I got--

576
00:29:47,130 --> 00:29:47,930
不是吧
Oh, come on!

577
00:29:47,930 --> 00:29:48,670
怎么了
What?

578
00:29:48,670 --> 00:29:50,970
武器装置没连上
The weapons won't come online.

579
00:29:50,970 --> 00:29:52,130
为什么
Why not?

580
00:29:52,130 --> 00:29:53,170
我不知道
I don't know.

581
00:29:53,170 --> 00:29:55,570
那就找原因  我们需要飞弹
Well, figure it out. we need those drones.

582
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:03,500
她在哪里
Where is she?

583
00:30:04,700 --> 00:30:06,170
我们不知道
We don't know.

584
00:30:06,170 --> 00:30:07,330
我们都找遍了
We searched everywhere.

585
00:30:07,330 --> 00:30:09,570
你是想说她就这样消失了吗
Are you telling me she just disappeared?

586
00:30:09,770 --> 00:30:12,600
我是说我们找遍了几乎
I'm saying that we searched every room and corridor

587
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:13,830
每个房间和走道
Within the stun field.

588
00:30:13,830 --> 00:30:16,170
哪儿都找不到
We couldn't find her anywhere.

589
00:30:16,170 --> 00:30:18,200
她对这个城市很了解
She knows this city well.

590
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:20,230
一定是躲在哪里了
She's hiding somewhere.

591
00:30:20,230 --> 00:30:21,570
她在和我玩
